column3: The *third* HDMI port from the left.\r\n  Labeled J5 and HDMI In 1.\r\n
The *fourth* HDMI port from the left. (Closest to the USB.)\r\n  Labeled J4 and HDMI In 2.\r\n
The *first* HDMI port from the left.\r\n  Labeled J3 and HDMI Out 1.\r\n
The *second* HDMI port from the left.\r\n  Labeled J2 and HDMI Out 2.\r\n
